high_descs: Turn right, walk to bath tub
Pick up bottle from side of tub
Take a left, walk one or two steps, take left to face toilet
Place bottle on top of toilet tank
Take left, walk away from toilet, take right, take another right to sink
Open the second cupboard from right, pick up bottle
Turn back to tub, take left, Bring bottle to toilet
Place bottle to left of the other bottle
anns.task_desc: Bring two bottles to the toilet tank

high_descs: turn to the right and walk over to the bathtub ahead of you
grab the soap dispenser off of the bathroom tub
turn around and face the bathroom toilet
place the soap dispenser on top of the toilet
turn left and walk forwards a bit, then hang a right and walk over to the kitchen sink on your right
grab the soap dispenser out from underneath the right side sink
turn to the right and walk over to the right side of the toilet
place the soap dispenser on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: place two soap dispensers on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the tub.
Pick up the pump bottle on the tub lid.
Turn left and walk to the right side of the toilet bowl.
Place the bottle on the toilet tank
Walk around the toilet to the closest sink and face it.
Take the pump bottle out of the bottom left cabinet.
Walk around the toilet back to the right side of it.
Place the bottle to the left of the other bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place two pump bottles on a toilet tank.
